queries.sql: SELECT `tbl_user`.*, CONCAT('',COALESCE(jd7b51640.type, ''),'') as sd7b51640, CONCAT('',COALESCE(jc76a5e84.status, ''),'') as sc76a5e84 FROM `tbl_user` LEFT JOIN `user_type` as `jd7b51640` ON `jd7b51640`.`type` = `tbl_user`.`user_type` LEFT JOIN `user_status` as `jc76a5e84` ON `jc76a5e84`.`status` = `tbl_user`.`active` LIMIT 10
